          "description": "Create a client/ directory with a React app (Vite + React + TypeScript). Install @mui/material, @emotion/react, @emotion/styled. Build a single-page chat UI: a text input at the bottom, a scrollable message history above it, and a Send button. Use MUI components (Box, TextField, Button, Paper, Typography). Color scheme: ocean (primary blue tones). Font: Inter. On submit, POST to /api/chat and display the agent's response in the message list. Show a loading state while waiting.",
